159
00:16:56,016 --> 00:16:57,266
¡Davis!

160
00:16:57,392 --> 00:16:59,059
Aquí estoy.

161
00:16:59,185 --> 00:17:00,269
¡Eddie!

162
00:17:00,478 --> 00:17:02,187
¡Aquí!

163
00:17:04,024 --> 00:17:06,358
